{"tid":1380422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 下次點譴責?","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T04:39:15.000Z","uid":293274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ee213c36b29500db588f5f37a273ecf573b0c714","tid":1380422,"uid":293274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:20:06.000Z","msg":"毅進仔冇貨喇，幫下手<br />\n<br />\n超嚴厲譴責<br />\n極嚴厲譴責<br />\n終極嚴厲譴責<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/29/P2019072900116.htm?fbclid=IwAR3ak9P5MjyDUMyYyKz4a-ogWZSokwexiA-TRnaHAtL2g2PxBwd_BIQ9DOA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201907%2F29%2FP2019072900116.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3ak9P5MjyDUMyYyKz4a-ogWZSokwexiA-TRnaHAtL2g2PxBwd_BIQ9DOA&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67azbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=07c58d11\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/29/P2019072900116.htm?fbclid=IwAR3ak9P5MjyDUMyYyKz4a-ogWZSokwexiA-TRnaHAtL2g2PxBwd_BIQ9DOA</a><br />\n<br />\n激進示威者破壞法紀 警方予以最嚴厲譴責<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  昨日（七月二十八日）在西營盤和上環一帶的示威活動中，一批激進示威者作出違法行為，大規模破壞政府公物、四處縱火、使用多樣致命武器襲擊警察。警方予以最嚴厲的譴責。<br />\n<br />\n[......]<br />\n  激進示威者的行為越演越烈，由最初拆鐵欄、擲鐵枝和磚頭，及至到處縱火和大肆破壞。該等行為已經嚴重偏離和平表達訴求的原則，警方予以強烈譴責。警隊有決心、有能力，將違法人士繩之於法。 <br />\n <br />\n完"},{"pid":"211b5e7ad48f99576456ac61522fde5dd04274df","tid":1380422,"uid":72943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:39:15.000Z","msg":"元朗班白衫就無能力調派人員支援<br />\n示威者就有決心有能力拘捕"}]}